snippet.title: Mortal Kombat 1 – Invasions Season 4 Trailer
snippet.description:
An army of Ultra Mileenas? That’s a dream and a nightmare all wrapped into one. Season of the Huntress is now live! She’ll be waiting. #MK1

Get the Premium Edition today and jump into Invasions Mode: https://www.mortalkombat.com/purchase

It's In Our Blood. Discover a reborn Mortal Kombat Universe created by Fire God Liu Kang. Mortal Kombat 1 ushers in a new era of the iconic franchise with a new fighting system, game modes, and Fatalities!
